replyContent: Hi. The app will perform auto-focus and lock the focus once you press record. The best way to get your image perfect is to have someone (or something) on-screen and press record when the image is clear - this will lock the focus and you can then move off-screen. We are working on a 'lock focus' button and will be available shortly.

content: Hi. I got the app today. When I go to record, the person becomes fuzzy. They're not fuzzy when I'm not recording. Is there a fix for this? Otherwise I'll need a refund. 😔
replyContent: Hi Debra. The app will lock focus when hitting record, before this it will auto-focus. I recommend starting recording when a person is in view and clear, at this point the focus is locked and you can move off screen. We are thinking of introducing a 'focus lock' button to do a similar thing if there is enough interest.
